{{/_docs-example}}

<h3>Word break</h3>

<p>Prevent long strings of text from breaking your componentsâ€™ layout by using .uom-text-break to set word-wrap: break-word and word-break: break-word. We use word-wrap instead of the more common overflow-wrap for wider browser support, and add the deprecated word-break: break-word to avoid issues with flex containers.</p>

